metadata.name: Troubled Mind
metadata.description:
Troubled mind, Troubled Mind
Come back before time passes by,
If I show you my troubled mind,
Will you show yours too in time.
You see only a bit of what I show,
No more can you see,
Because that will blur your mind.

Troubled mind, Troubled mind,
It's time to come out of the blur,
Stitch yourself in time,
Because that is what it means to be healed in time.

Worry not, because I am here,
And million of things to heal you dear.
